suncertify.db
Class URLyBirdFieldParsers

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.db.URLyBirdFieldParsers
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, FieldParsers
public final class URLyBirdFieldParsers
extends java.lang.Object
implements FieldParsers

A collection of parsers for fields in the URLyBird database file format. The properties file can contain the date format for parsing date values, and the "true" and "false" values for parsing boolean values.
